(4898, 'Strato h 30 ml mouth spray', 'ستراتو اتش 30 مل بخاخ', '', '78', 'Chlorhexidine gluconate+hyaluronic acid+propolis extract+thymus extract+liquorice extract+chamomile extract+clove oil+lidocaine', 'Nutrisynth for trade and distribution', 'Spray', 'بخاخ', '', 'Mouth spray', '30 ml', 'Chlorhexidine is available over-the-counter in various formulations (e.g. solution, sponge, cloth, swab) as a topical antiseptic to sanitize prior to surgeries and/or medical procedures.[L11518,L11521,L11527,L11533] Dental formulations, available by prescription only, include an oral rinse indicated for the treatment of gingivitis[L11512] and a slow-release "chip" which is inserted into periodontal pockets and is indicated for the reduction of pocket depth in adult patients with periodontitis as an adjunct therapy to dental scaling and root planing procedures.[L11536]', '', '', 838, '2025-06-21', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(19879, 'Glopamil 120mg s.r.caps.', 'جلوباميل اس ار 120 مجم كبسولات', '', '5', 'Verapamil', 'Global napi pharmaceuticals', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Antihypertensive.cardioselective calcium chennel blocker', '120mg', 'Verapamil is indicated in the treatment of vasopastic (i.e. Prinzmetal''s) angina, unstable angina, and chronic stable angina. It is also indicated to treat hypertension, for the prophylaxis of repetitive paroxysmal supraventricular tachycardia, and in combination with digoxin to control ventricular rate in patients with atrial fibrillation or atrial flutter.[L8791] Given intravenously, it is indicated for the treatment of various supraventricular tachyarrhythmias, including rapid conversion to sinus rhythm in patients with supraventricular tachycardia and for temporary control of ventricular rate in patients with atrial fibrillation or atrial flutter.[L10481]
